  "description": "Kiyo and Sumire came to Kyoto from Aomori Prefecture, dreaming of becoming maiko. But after an unexpected turn of events, Kiyo starts working as the live-in cook at the Maiko House. Their story unfolds in Kagai, the Geiko and maiko district in Kyoto, alongside their housemate maikos. Kiyo nourishes them daily with her homecooked meals, and Sumire strives toward her promising future as the once-in-a-century maiko.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Crunchyroll)<br>\n<br>\n<i>Note: Each episode was released on the fourth Thursday of each month. One episode usually features three chapters.</i>",
